node.title: Two die, two injured in crash in eastern Bay of Plenty
node.description: Two people have been killed in a two-vehicle crash on a section of SH2 at Waiotahe, near Ōpōtiki this afternoon.
node.content:
["Two people have been killed in a two-vehicle crash on a section of State Highway 2 at Waiotahe, near \u014cp\u014dtiki this afternoon.", "", "
\nPhoto: Supplied / St John Ambulance\n
", "Another two people were injured in the crash, which involved a van and a ute.", "Emergency services were called to the scene at around 2.30pm.", "The intersection of SH2 and Ohiwa Beach Road remains closed, police say.", "Motorists are asked to continue to follow the detours in place.", "Northbound traffic is being diverted down Waitotahe Valley Road and southbound traffic is being diverted down Paerata Ridge Road.", "Waka Kotahi has warned of delays for motorists."]
